Privacy Policy for "Правда или Ложь"
Effective Date: 20.01.2025

Introduction
Thank you for using "Правда или Ложь" (the "Game"). Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our Game. By accessing or using the Game, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
1. Information You Provide
Contact Information: If you contact us through support channels, we may collect your email address or other contact details.
In-Game Data: Optional information such as usernames or scores may be collected to enhance gameplay experience.
2. Automatically Collected Information
Device Information: We may collect information about the device you use to access the Game, such as device type, operating system, and unique identifiers.
Usage Data: Information about how you interact with the Game, including gameplay statistics, session durations, and error reports.
3. Third-Party Services
If the Game uses third-party services (e.g., analytics or advertising), these services may collect additional information as per their privacy policies.

How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:

Provide and improve the Game.
Analyze gameplay and usage trends to improve user experience.
Fix bugs, errors, and ensure the Game runs smoothly.
Communicate with you for support or updates.
Sharing Your Information
We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except:

With Service Providers: To perform Game-related services such as analytics or hosting.
When Required by Law: If legally required to disclose information to comply with applicable laws or regulations.
Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Your Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:

Access and Correction: Request access to or correction of your personal data.
Deletion: Request deletion of your data, subject to certain legal obligations.
Opt-Out: Disable data collection for analytics or targeted advertising.
To exercise these rights, please contact us at pegasusstudio.info@gmail.com.

Children’s Privacy
The Game is not intended for children under the age of 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child without parental consent, we will delete it immediately. Parents or guardians may contact us at [Insert Contact Email].

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and the "Effective Date" will be updated accordingly. Please review this page periodically for updates.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:

Email: pegasusstudio.info@gmail.com
